    25 				; Define ramzap as required in the outer source file.
    26 				; If ramzap is not defined, no additional code is generated.
    27 				; If ramzap is 0, NOPs are generated that do not harm the program in RAM
    28 				; If ramzap is 1, zap code is generated that kills the program in RAM
    29 				;ramzap	equ	1	; to zap or not to zap, that is the question?
